Actors: Thiago Rosseti, Bruna Cavalieri, Marcos Caruso, Jonas Bloch
Writer: Melanie Dimantas (adaptation), Ronaldo Santos (adaptation), Lúcia Machado de Almeida (novel)
Title: O Escaravelho do Diabo
Plot: A series of crimes against redheads scares the people from a little town. After the death of his brother, the 13 year old Alberto decides to investigate what is happening and is helped by the experienced, but forgotten, Inspector Pimentel.
